From: Neelesh Gupta <neelegup@linux.vnet.ibm.com>
Subject: [PATCH] powerpc/powernv: Enable fetching of platform sensor data
Git-commit: 7224adbbb80329d1a3ec5aa98213b50365fcd246
Patch-mainline: v3.15-rc1
References: bnc#878240,FATE#315784,bnc#875242

This patch enables fetching of various platform sensor data through
OPAL and expects a sensor handle from the driver to pass to OPAL.

Signed-off-by: Neelesh Gupta <neelegup@linux.vnet.ibm.com>
Signed-off-by: Benjamin Herrenschmidt <benh@kernel.crashing.org>
Acked-by: Torsten Duwe <duwe@suse.de>

